---
By: Epictetus
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 25
    Verse: 4
Tags:
  - Anxiety
---
Do you wish to live in tension? By no means. No one who is in a state of
fear or sorrow or tension is free, but whoever is delivered from sorrows or
fears or anxieties, he is at the same time delivered from servitude.
